# SteamScore JSON API (v1)

# Group Achievements

## List [GET /achievements]

+ Response 200 (application/vnd.api+json)
    + Attributes (Base Response)
        - links
            - self: `https://api.steamscore.info/achievements`

## View [GET /achievements/{id}]

+ Parameters
    - id: `355dc04d-6f57-4140-adb5-8fc4be7175b1` (string, required) - Unique identifier of the achievement.

+ Response 200 (application/vnd.api+json)
    + Attributes (Base Response)
        - links
            - self: `https://api.steamscore.info/achievements/355dc04d-6f57-4140-adb5-8fc4be7175b1`

