# Group Users

## List [GET /users]

+ Response 200 (application/vnd.api+json)
    + Attributes (Base Response)
        - links
            - self: https://api.steamscore.info/users
        - data (array[User], required)

## View [GET /users/{id}]

+ Parameters
    - id: `33c1d637-8c1e-4e83-9de9-167a4d8993c5` (string, required) - Unique identifier of the user.

+ Response 200 (application/vnd.api+json)
    + Attributes (Base Response)
        - links
            - self: `https://api.steamscore.info/users/33c1d637-8c1e-4e83-9de9-167a4d8993c5`
        - data (User, required)

# Data Structures

## Base Response (object, fixed-type)

- links (object, required)
    - self (string, required)
- jsonapi (object, required, fixed-type)
    - version: 1.0 (enum[string], required, default)
        - 1.0

## User (object, fixed-type)

- type: `users` (enum[string], required, default)
    - `users`
- id: `33c1d637-8c1e-4e83-9de9-167a4d8993c5` (string, required)
- attributes (object, required)
